'''热带风暴尚塔尔'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Chantal}}）是[[2007年大西洋飓风季|2007年大西洋飓风季]]形成的一场持续时间较为短暂的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]，也是该季第3场热带风暴。系统于7月31日在[[百慕大|百慕大]]和[[鳕鱼角|鳕鱼角]]之间成形，其前身不具备[[热带气旋|热带天气系统特征]]，然后因外界环境有利而迅速达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度。气旋加速向东北方向移动，行经海域[[海面温度|水温]]逐渐降低，风暴对流随之减弱，于8月1日清晨开始转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]也随即停止针对系统发布公告。不久后，尚塔尔的温带残留穿越[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]东南部上空，然后进入北太平洋开放水域。

风暴的前身在[[百慕大|百慕大]]产生中等程度降水，成为温带系统后，尚塔尔的残留又令[[阿瓦隆半岛|阿瓦隆半岛]]各地普遍出现强烈阵风和暴雨，引起洪灾和风害，投保损失共计约有2500万[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]（2007年加拿大元，相当于2007年的2430万美元）。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Chantal 2007 track.png}}
7月21日，一片[[冷锋|锋面天气系统]]离开[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]，并在向东南方向飘流期间退化成[[低压槽|低压槽]]，到7月26日时，位于[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]以东的系统已基本停止移动。系统内起初未能保持深层[[对流|对流]]，但多名气象学家还是从7月28日开始采用[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]进行追踪。系统向东北方向前进，<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Chantal Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-02-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL032007_Chantal.pdf | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011406/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL032007_Chantal.pdf | deadurl = no | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | date =  }}</ref>但由于外界环境不利，其结构起初杂乱无章。不过，气象机构预计系统行经海域大气环境会朝有利于[[热带气旋|热带天气系统]]发展的方向变化<ref name="729two">{{cite report | author = Mainelli | year = 2007 | title = July 29 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]]}}</ref>，到7月29日时，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]已认定系统有发展成热带或[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的潜力<ref name="729two2">{{cite report | author = Blake | year = 2007 | title = July 29 Tropical Weather Outlook (2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。7月30日，低气压在大规模中纬度低压槽的影响下继续向东北方向前进，并从[[百慕大|百慕大]]以西洋面经过。系统包含部分暴露在外的下层环流，偶尔会被东北方向持续存在的对流区包裹起来。到了7月31日清晨，多艘船只测得的数量和[[快速散射仪|快速散射仪]]卫星观察结果都表明系统风速达到每小时55公里，其中心已经关联有足够对流，美国国家飓风中心因此将位于百慕大[[罗盘方位|西北偏北]]方向约435公里海域、[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[巴恩斯特布尔县|巴恩斯特布尔县]][[查塔姆_(马萨诸塞州)|查塔姆]]（{{lang|en|Chatham}}）东南偏南方向约710公里洋面的系统归类为第三号热带低气压。<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Depression Three Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-02-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002122325/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>

成为热带低气压后，气旋的下层中心依然部分暴露在外，深层对流主要分布在东北半圆内。风暴所处洋面[[海面温度|水温]]约有27[[摄氏温标|°C]]，有气象学家认为，低气压有可能在达到热带风暴强度后转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。<ref name="disc2">{{cite report | author = Mainelli | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Depression Three Discussion Two | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002122336/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-02-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.002.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>中心上空的对流继续增长，低气压因此于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月31日早上6点左右在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]][[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]以南约855公里海域升级成热带风暴并获名“尚塔尔”（{{lang|en|Chantal}}）。受中层低压槽影响，气旋继续向东北方向前进<ref name="tcr" />并且很快就发展出层次分明的曲线[[雨带|带状特征]]<ref name="disc3">{{cite report |author=Blake |year=2007 |title=Tropical Storm Chantal Discussion Three |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2016-02-02 |archivedate=2016-01-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121071653/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.003.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.003.shtml? |deadurl=no |date= }}</ref>。成为热带风暴6小时后，尚塔尔达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />。接下来，气旋行经洋面的水温和大气温度都逐渐降低<ref name="disc4">{{cite report |author=Blake |year=2007 |title=Tropical Storm Chantal Discussion Four |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2016-02-02 |archivedate=2016-01-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121071653/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.004.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.004.shtml? |date= }}</ref>，对流因此逐渐减弱。环流同逐渐逼近的锋面天气系统融合，尚塔尔于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}8月1日早上6点转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。<ref name="tcr" />

成为温带气旋后，尚塔尔中心附近仍然保持有零散对流，但主要的对流区和云系已经扩展到北翼<ref name="chc">{{cite report | author = PJB | year = 2007 | title = Post-Tropical Storm Chantal Information Statement at 3:00 AM ADT Wednesday August 1, 2007 | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | accessdate = 2011-06-11 | format = [[TXT|TXT]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611123132/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070801061030.Chantal.txt.en | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070801061030.Chantal.txt.en | archivedate = 2011-06-11 | deadurl = yes | date =  }}</ref>。8月1日中午时分，气旋沿[[阿瓦隆半岛|阿瓦隆半岛]]吹袭[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]，并以最高强度袭击[[普拉森提亚_(纽芬兰和拉不拉多)|普拉森提亚]]（{{lang|en|Placentia}}）地区<ref name="chc3">{{cite report | author1 = Fogarty | author2 = Roussel | year = 2007 | title = Post-Tropical Storm Chantal Intermediate Information Statement at 12:30 PM ADT Wednesday August 1, 2007 | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | accessdate = 2007-08-01 | archivedate = 2011-06-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611123144/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070801145621.Chantal.txt.en | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070801145621.Chantal.txt.en | format = TXT | deadurl = yes | date =  }}</ref>。接下来，气旋风速提高到飓风强度。8月3日，尚塔尔的温带残留在北大西洋最北侧进入再度减弱，于8月5日与[[冰岛|冰岛]]以东的另一个温带气旋合并。<ref name="tcr" />

== 影响 ==
[[File:Flood_brook.jpg|thumb]]
发展成尚塔尔的[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]从7月30日就开始影响[[百慕大|百慕大]]，空中云层增多，还出现局部暴风雨。次日，系统从该岛以西经过并产生更多降水，[[百慕大国际机场|百慕大国际机场]]的两天合计降雨量为53.8毫米，相当于月度降雨总量的35%。岛上还出现[[雷暴|雷暴]]，测得的最高风速为每小时72公里。<ref>{{cite news |author=Bermuda Weather Service |year=2007 |title=Sunny beginning, wet ending... |accessdate=2007-08-01 |url=http://www.weather.bm/climatereport/climateReport.asp#jsAnchor |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070808041105/http://www.weather.bm/climatereport/climateReport.asp#jsAnchor |archivedate=2007-08-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>尚塔尔离开百慕大后，北大西洋开放海域一艘呼号为“{{lang|en|C}}60{{lang|en|Y}}4”的船只测得每小时59公里的持续风速<ref name="disc2" />。{{lang|en|UTC}}7月31日晚上23点左右，新斯科舍东南方向洋面的一个浮标在尚塔尔从附近掠过时测得995[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]）的[[气压|气压]]值<ref name="disc5">{{cite report |author=Brown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121071653/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.005.shtml |year=2007 |title=Tropical Storm Chantal Discussion Five |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2016-02-02 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al03/al032007.discus.005.shtml? |archivedate=2016-01-21 |deadurl=no |date= }}</ref>。

尚塔尔成为热带风暴后不久，加拿大大西洋风暴预测中心向纽芬兰岛沿海地区发布烈风警告<ref name="chc1">{{cite report | author = PJB | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Chantal Information Statement at 9:00 AM ADT Tuesday July 31, 2007 | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | accessdate = 2011-06-11 | archivedate = 2011-06-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611123017/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070731120427.Chantal.txt.en | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070731120427.Chantal.txt.en | deadurl = yes | format = TXT | date =  }}</ref>。纽芬兰拉不拉多气象办公室之后也向纽芬兰岛发布暴雨警告<ref name="chc2">{{cite report |author=PJB |year=2007 |title=Tropical Storm Chantal Information Statement at 3:30 PM ADT Tuesday July 31, 2007 |publisher=Canadian Hurricane Centre |accessdate=2007-08-01 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5QktdY2Lg?url=http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070731180027.Chantal.txt.en |url=http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070731180027.Chantal.txt.en |archivedate=2007-07-31 |deadurl=yes |format=TXT |date= }}</ref>。当地近海水域浪出现高达6米的狂浪，陆地上的风力达到中等强度，风暴上岸地点附近测得时速88公里阵风，但这一数据没有得到官方认可。尚塔尔的残留在快速穿越纽芬兰岛期间也产生暴雨，[[圣约翰斯_(纽芬兰-拉布拉多)|圣约翰斯西]]在1小时内就降下43毫米雨量，是这场风暴1小时降雨量最多的地方。总降雨量最高的则是[[阿真舍|阿真舍]]（{{lang|en|Argentia}}），达200.4毫米。降水引发洪灾，阿瓦隆半岛有多个城镇的街道被冲毁。<ref name="chcfinal">{{cite web | author = Fogarty | year = 2007 | title = Post-Tropical Storm Chantal Intermediate Information Statement at 6:30 PM ADT Wednesday August 1, 2007 | publisher = Canadian Hurricane Centre | accessdate = 2011-06-11 | archivedate = 2011-06-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611123023/http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070801202538.Chantal.txt.en | url = http://www.atl.ec.gc.ca/weather/hurricane/bulletins/20070801202538.Chantal.txt.en | format = TXT }}</ref>

洪水导致[[希普_(纽芬兰与拉布拉多)|希普]]（{{lang|en|Ship Harbour}}）同外界的交通中断，情况持续5天后才因临时道路通行而改善。[[西班牙人湾|西班牙人湾]]（{{lang|en|Spaniard's Bay}}）的一座桥梁因洪水而垮塌约50厘米<ref name="cns802">{{cite news |author=Ken Meaney |year=2007 |title=Newfoundlanders mopping up after Chantal |url=http://www.canada.com/nationalpost/news/story.html?id=e59e5737-a987-40c5-8d38-6d27d7d76458&k=78928 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121071654/http://www.canada.com/nationalpost/news/story.html?id=e59e5737-a987-40c5-8d38-6d27d7d76458&k=78928 |publisher=CanWest News Service |accessdate=2016-02-02 |archivedate=2016-01-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，临时桥梁在两个月内就已建成，永久替换原桥的新桥在2008年夏建成<ref>{{cite news | author = Lillian Simmons | date = 2007-08-28 | title = Towns bite into bridgework | publisher = The Transcontinental Compass}}</ref>。该国遭受的投保损失共计达2500万[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]（2007年加拿大元，相当于2007年的2430万美元）<ref>{{cite news | author = Siri Agrell | publisher = The Globe and Mail | date = 2010-09-23 | title = St. John's cleans up following Hurricane Igor | url = http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/st-johns-cleans-up-following-hurricane-igor/article1213895/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202151311/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/st-johns-cleans-up-following-hurricane-igor/article1213895/ | accessdate = 2016-02-02 | archivedate = 2016-02-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

